**** {{ill|Magoroku Onsen|ja|孫六温泉|12=draft}}
**** {{ill|Ipponmatsu Onsen|ja|一本松温泉|12=draft}}
**** {{ill|Kaniba Onsen|ja|蟹場温泉|12=draft}}
**** {{ill|Ōgama Onsen|ja|大釜温泉|12=draft}}
**** {{ill|Tsurunoyu Onsen|ja|鶴の湯温泉|12=draft}}

